    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "The du command is used to estimate file space usage.",
      "html": "<p>The <code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">du</span></code> command is used to estimate file space usage.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "It's helpful for finding out how much space files and directories take up.",
      "html": "<p>It's helpful for finding out how much space files and directories take up.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "All examples below use a hypothetical output for demonstration:",
